com.mobilerq.android.sdk

Interface MrqDataProvider


  • public interface MrqDataProvider
    An interface specifying a type that MrqSdk will use to retrieve the user's current context.

    Users of MrqSdk must implement this interface in order to provide information about the user to the SDK.

    See Also:
    MrqUserContext

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      MrqUserContext currentUserContext()
      Retrieve the user's current context.

      • currentUserContext

        MrqUserContext currentUserContext()
        Retrieve the user's current context. This method should be implemented to return a new instance of MrqUserContext that represents the user's current context.
        Returns:
        the user's current context
